timelineItems.name: Columbus Crew
timelineItems.text: 101’: CHANCE - Speas takes a rip from the top of Chicago’s area but Johnson is there to save. #Crew96 #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: Columbus Crew
timelineItems.text: 103’: CHANCE - Anor takes a shot, another Johnson save. @ChicagoFire still leading 3-2 in extra time. #USOC2014

timelineItems.comment: First Half Extra Time ends, Chicago Fire 3, Columbus Crew 2.

timelineItems.name: Chicago Fire
timelineItems.text: 106' - Second period of extra time is underway.... #cf97 3, #Crew96 2 WATCH: http://t.co/cW9YdudNmu #USOC2014 #CHIvCLB #MLS

timelineItems.name: Columbus Crew
timelineItems.text: 106’: Second extra-time period is underway. #Crew96 #CF97 #USOC2014

timelineItems.comment: Second Half Extra Time begins Chicago Fire 3, Columbus Crew 2.

timelineItems.name: Chicago Fire
timelineItems.text: 108' - GOALLLLLLLLLLLLLL Anangono! 4-2 #cf97! #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: Chicago Fire
timelineItems.text: ON THE GOAL: Alex finds space on the left and crosses for Anangono who one-times past Clark for his second of the match. #cf97 #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: Chicago Fire
timelineItems.text: FULL-TIME! Extra time goals from Amarikwa, Anangono give Fire a 4-2 win tonight over #Crew96! #cf97 #USOC2014 #CHIvCLB

timelineItems.name: Chicago Fire
timelineItems.text: Your #cf97 Man of the Match is @JLanangono13! #cf97 #USOC2014 #CHIvCLB

timelineItems.name: Chicago Fire
timelineItems.text: Fire advance to a quarterfinal #USOC2014 date July 8/9 @ATLSilverbacks! #cf97

timelineItems.comment: Second Half Extra Time ends, Chicago Fire 4, Columbus Crew 2.
Match ends, Chicago Fire 4, Columbus Crew 2.

timelineItems.name: Chicago Fire
timelineItems.text: 27' - Fire have had the better of the play but are locked 0-0 with #Crew96 in #USOC2014. WATCH: http://t.co/OpNx1RUHOB #cf97 #CHIvCLB

timelineItems.name: Columbus Crew
timelineItems.text: 31’: Magee fighting for the ball inside #Crew96’s area, but Wahl makes a nice play to clear the danger. Still scoreless. #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: Columbus Crew
timelineItems.text: 35’: Ianni makes it 1-0 #CF97, with Shipp getting the assist on the free kick. #Crew96 trailing in this #USOC2014 Fifth Round match.

timelineItems.name: Columbus Crew
timelineItems.text: HALFTIME - @ChicagoFire 1 - #Crew96 0. Black & Gold trail at the break following Ianni’s goal. #USOC2014

timelineItems.comment: First Half ends, Chicago Fire 1, Columbus Crew 0.

timelineItems.name: Columbus Crew
timelineItems.text: One halftime substitute for #Crew96 - Arrieta is replacing Meram. All other personnel remain the same. #USOC2014

timelineItems.comment: Second Half begins Chicago Fire 1, Columbus Crew 0.

timelineItems.name: Columbus Crew
timelineItems.text: 46’: We’re back for the second half. LIVE STREAM: http://t.co/buamw1dHRm. #Crew96 #CF97 #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: Major League Soccer
timelineItems.text: Take a bow, Arrieta. #USOC2014 #CHIvCLB http://t.co/cUm2Z0a0ff

timelineItems.name: Chicago Fire
timelineItems.text: Just over an hour gone and #CHIvCLB is locked 1-1 here @ToyotaPark. WATCH: http://t.co/OpNx1RUHOB #cf97 #Crew96 #USOC2014 #MLS

timelineItems.name: Major League Soccer
timelineItems.text: A 2013 #USOC100 rematch. This gnarly thunderstorm postponed #CHIvCLB last year. http://t.co/VrAnWUDKX1

timelineItems.text: A 2013 #USOC100 rematch. This gnarly thunderstorm postponed #CHIvCLB last year. http://t.co/VrAnWUDKX1

timelineItems.text: Moments from going LIVE for #CHIvCLB in #USOC2014! WATCH: http://t.co/e8lo4WmRjH #cf97 #MLS

timelineItems.name: Chicago Fire
timelineItems.text: We're LIVE with pre-roll for tonight's #CHIvCLB #USOC2014 match! WATCH: http://t.co/OpNx1RUHOB #cf97 #MLS @USOpenCup

timelineItems.name: Columbus Crew
timelineItems.text: We are about ready for kickoff at Toyota Park for tonight’s #USOC2014 clash vs. @ChicagoFire. WATCH: http://t.co/p1IlE6NJnt. #Crew96

timelineItems.name: Columbus Crew
timelineItems.text: Anthem is done. Lineups have been announced. We’re ready to roll. #USOC2014 #Crew96 #CF97

timelineItems.name: Chicago Fire
timelineItems.text: Fire look to book a #USOC2014 quarterfinal date with @ATLSilverbacks now. WATCH: http://t.co/OpNx1RUHOB, FOLLOW @ChiFireMatch #cf97

timelineItems.comment: Lineups are announced and players are warming up.

timelineItems.name: Chicago Fire
timelineItems.text: 75' - Fire trail Columbus 2-1... Tune in: http://t.co/OpNx1RUHOB #cf97 #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: Chicago Fire
timelineItems.text: 83' - ON THE GOAL: Watson waltzes into the box on the right, crosses for Anangono who beats Clark one-time. 2-2! #cf97 #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: Chicago Fire
timelineItems.text: FT. At the end of 90 minutes we're locked at 2-2... We're headed to extra time. #cf97 #USOC2014 #Crew96 WATCH: http://t.co/e8lo4WmRjH

First Half Extra Time begins Chicago Fire 2, Columbus Crew 2.
